item.title: CVE-2023-46652|2024-09-17T13:41:16.898Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20lambdatest-automation%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins lambdatest-automation Plugin 1.20.9 and earlier allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to enumerate credentials IDs of LAMBDATEST credentials stored in Jenkins.
